              "textEn": "<b>Lesson 7 • Discussing bad results</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "Ron, Alex, and Pam work for Brooklyn Brewski, a company that brews and distributes beer throughout New York. The company's recent results have been terrible."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Alex:</b> We need to "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "face the music",
              "word": "face the music"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "here. We're"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "in deep trouble",
              "word": "in deep trouble"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "! Sales are down by 50 percent versus last year."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Pam:</b> It looks like we're going to be"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "in the red",
              "word": "in the red"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "for the year "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "to the tune of",
              "word": "to the tune of"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "$1 million."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ron:</b>"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "no wonder",
              "word": "no wonder",
              "textEn": ". We're losing"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "market share",
              "word": "market share"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "to Manhattan Beer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Alex:</b> Why? We need to "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "get to the bottom of",
              "word": "get to the bottom of"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "this!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Pam:</b> Every year they come up with beers. They're really"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "on top of trends",
              "word": "on top of trends"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". For instance, last year they released a low-carb beer."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ron:</b> No wonder they're"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "eating one's lunch",
              "word": "eating our lunch"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "! They're "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "cash in on",
              "word": "cashing in on"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "the latest trends and"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "bring a product to market",
              "word": "bring great new products to market"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Pam:</b> Meanwhile, we're"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "run in place",
              "word": "running in place"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". We need a new product line and new ideas for marketing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Alex:</b> It's time to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "clean house",
              "word": "clean house"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "and bring some "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "new blood",
              "word": "new blood"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "into this company."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ron:</b> "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "You took the words right out of my mouth",
              "word": "You took the words right out of my mouth"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "! We need some new people with fresh ideas."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
